{{nihongo|'''Matsuko Deluxe'''|<U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9>|Matsuko Derakkusu|born October 26, 1972 in [[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]]}} is a gay Japanese [[columnist]], [[essayist]], and ''[[tarento]]'' known for his [[cross-dressing]] stage persona. In 2010, he became known for his "feud" with many of Japan's female television announcers over their perceived image.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://japan.techinsight.jp/2010/07/matsuko_0721.html |title=Techinsight <U+00BB> <U+3010><U+30A8><U+30F3><U+30BF><U+304C><U+30D3><U+30BF><U+30DF><U+30F3><U+266A><U+3011><U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9><U+304C><U+6CB8><U+9A30><U+5BF8><U+524D><U+FF01> <U+201C><U+5929><U+6575><U+201D><U+5973><U+5B50><U+30A2><U+30CA><U+3068><U+30D0><U+30C8><U+30EB><U+3002><U+30DF><U+30C3><U+30C4><U+30FB><U+30DE><U+30F3><U+30B0><U+30ED><U+30FC><U+30D6><U+3082><U+53C2><U+6226><U+3002> |publisher=Japan.techinsight.jp |date=2010-07-22 |accessdate=2013-03-28}}</ref> Matsuko was also critical of then [[Politics of Tokyo|Tokyo Prefectural Governor]] [[Shintaro Ishihara]]'s legislation to limit the sales of [[manga]] and [[anime]] to those under 18 as well as the governor's noted disdain of [[homosexuality]] and [[transvestitism]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.j-cast.com/2010/12/14083475.html |title=<U+77F3><U+539F><U+90FD><U+77E5><U+4E8B><U+306B><U+300C><U+3042><U+306E><U+767A><U+8A00><U+306F><U+72C2><U+3063><U+3066><U+308B><U+FF01><U+300D> <U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9><U+3001><U+9752><U+5C11><U+5E74><U+6761><U+4F8B><U+3067><U+6FC0><U+6012> (1/2) : J-CAST<U+30CB><U+30E5><U+30FC><U+30B9> |publisher=J-cast.com |date=2010-12-14 |accessdate=2013-03-28}}</ref>

Matsuko is a regular panelist and sometimes host on the Japanese talk shows ''[[Goji ni Much<U+016B>!]]'', ''[[HONMADEKKA!?TV]]'', ''[[Shirushiru Mishiru]]'', ''[[Matsuko & Ariyoshi's Angry New Party]]'',<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariyoshi Hiroyuki and Matsuko Deluxe team up on late night television|url=http://www.tokyohive.com/2011/04/ariyoshi-hiroyuki-and-matsuko-deluxe-team-up-on-late-night-television/|work=Tokyo Hive||date=2011-04-04|accessdate=2012-07-08}}</ref> ''[[Jinsei ga Kawaru Ippunkan no Fuka Ii Hanashi]]'', ''[[Matsuko no Shiranai Sekai]]'', ''[[Arita & Matsuko & Man & Woman]]'', and ''[[Monday Late Show]]''. In 2013, Matsuko became part of an advertising campaign for [[Mister Donut]]'s 10th anniversary of introducing the "pon de ring" donut,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/video/2020394/full/ |title=<U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+3001><U+30E6><U+30C3><U+30AD><U+30FC><U+30CA><U+306B><U+6226><U+3005><U+6050><U+3005><U+300C><U+3068><U+3093><U+3067><U+3082><U+306A><U+3044><U+30DE><U+30DE><U+30BF><U+30EC><U+73FE><U+308C><U+305F><U+300D> (<U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9>) <U+30CB><U+30E5><U+30FC><U+30B9>-ORICON STYLE |publisher=Oricon.co.jp |date=2013-01-08 |accessdate=2013-03-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://natalie.mu/owarai/news/82761 |title=<U+304A><U+7B11><U+3044><U+30CA><U+30BF><U+30EA><U+30FC> - <U+30DD><U+30F3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30FB><U+30EA><U+30F3><U+30B0><U+30AE><U+30E3><U+30B0><U+300C><U+3082><U+3063><U+3061><U+FF01><U+300D><U+30C0><U+30F3><U+30C7><U+30A3><U+5742><U+91CE><U+6D41><U+884C><U+8A9E><U+72D9><U+3046> |publisher=Natalie.mu |date= |accessdate=2013-06-15}}</ref> and has continued being the company's spokesperson through its recipe renewal<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/news/confidence/2023809/full/ |title=<U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+3001><U+65E9><U+4E59><U+5973><U+FF06><U+897F><U+5C71><U+306E><U+201C><U+30C7><U+30AD><U+5A5A><U+201D><U+80AF><U+5B9A><U+300C><U+3067><U+304D><U+3061><U+3083><U+3063><U+305F><U+7D50><U+5A5A><U+304C><U+4E00><U+756A><U+697D><U+300D> (<U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9>) <U+30CB><U+30E5><U+30FC><U+30B9>-ORICON STYLE |publisher=Oricon.co.jp |date=2013-04-18 |accessdate=2013-06-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.excite.co.jp/News/entertainment_g/20130420/Narinari_20130420_21350.html |title=<U+30DF><U+30B9><U+30C9><U+65B0><U+65E7><U+98DF><U+3079><U+6BD4><U+3079><U+306B>4381<U+4EBA><U+3001><U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+30FB><U+30C7><U+30E9><U+30C3><U+30AF><U+30B9><U+201C><U+30DF><U+30B9><U+30C9><U+611B><U+201D><U+8A9E><U+308B><U+3002>(Narinari.com) - <U+30A8><U+30AD><U+30B5><U+30A4><U+30C8><U+30CB><U+30E5><U+30FC><U+30B9> |publisher=Excite.co.jp |date=2013-04-20 |accessdate=2013-06-15}}</ref> and [[Calpis]] collaboration promotions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tabetainjya.com/archives/food/_cm_47/ |title=<U+30DF><U+30B9><U+30C9><U+306E> <U+30AB><U+30EB><U+30D4><U+30B9><U+30B3><U+30E9><U+30DC><U+30C9><U+30FC><U+30CA><U+30C4><U+3001>CM<U+52D5><U+753B><U+3067><U+30DE><U+30C4><U+30B3><U+304C><U+4E00><U+6C17><U+306B><U+98F2><U+307F><U+5E72><U+3059> - <U+5E83><U+5CF6><U+30CB><U+30E5><U+30FC><U+30B9> <U+98DF><U+3079><U+30BF><U+30A4><U+30F3><U+30B8><U+30E3><U+30FC> |publisher=Tabetainjya.com |date=2013-06-15 |accessdate=2013-06-15}}</ref>

